== Faction ==
[[Scaven]]

== Location ==
Scaven Shielders may appear as hired support by completing a mission for any Scaven Settlement in Scaven Territory in Vulcore.

== Combat Strategy ==
Use Scaven Shielders as mobile cover to shield high-damage units. Their shield projection helps protect allies in the squad, and the dual Baron shields allow them to withstand considerable punishment.

